      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained, versatile SUV that perfectly balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated charcoal metallic that retains a high gloss; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, the body remains straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, featuring premium leather upholstery that shows only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the premium audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive logbook included. Recent work includes a fresh oil service and a cooling system flush performed within the last six months. The transmission shifts smoothly, and the engine runs quietly with no known leaks. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with plenty of depth remaining. This is a solid, reliable vehicle that has been cared for by a responsible owner and is ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
